
White Book: Mathematical Foundations & System Architecture of the CHRSy-AI System

---

Abstract

This white book presents the complete mathematical foundation and architectural specification for the Carbon dioxide Hydrogen Recovery System with AI Optimization (CHRSy-AI), a novel life support architecture for sustained human Mars exploration. We provide rigorous derivation of all governing equations, detailed control algorithms, and system architecture diagrams necessary for implementation. The document serves as both a theoretical foundation and technical specification for this paradigm-shifting approach to closed-loop life support.

