[1] Relevant study on RWGS reaction kinetics and carbon formation thresholds.
[2] Analysis of low-cycle thermal fatigue in aerospace materials.
[3] NASA/industry reports on high-temperature material performance for ISRU applications.
[4] Foundational papers on Model-Based Reinforcement Learning for control of complex systems.

